    "• Expert Review: Two endodontic specialists evaluated and refined the questions to ensure their accuracy and applicability.",
    "• Focused Approach: The study emphasized key decision points, like material selection and procedural sequencing, rather than addressing the full scope of RET.Between August 24, and September 2, 2024, the prepared questions were presented to three platforms: Gemini, GPT-4o, and ChatGPT-4 with a PDF plugin.",
    "The questions were asked by two different researchers using different accounts over a period of 10 days.",
    "The questions were posed three times a day, each time using the \"new conversation\" option (Fig. 2).",
    "The responses were recorded in an Excel spreadsheet (Microsoft, Redmond, WA, USA) and coded as correct, incorrect, or insufficient based on the guideline's criteria."
